JOLLY JOSE Jose Mourinho says Manchester United have learned ‘I am not the monster you say I am’ 
Special One says 'at least nobody runs away when I arrive at training' before later being pictured with face of thunder at the Lowry Hotel By Tom Sheen 3rd March 2017, 5:47 pm Updated: 3rd March 2017, 6:17 pm
